[
  {
    "text": "Macchiarini was a superstar surgeon.",
    "start": 0.667,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "He’s this good-looking man of mystery.",
    "start": 2.544,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "A miracle worker.",
    "start": 5.046,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "His technique was groundbreaking.",
    "start": 5.964,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "The artificial trachea",
    "start": 7.966,
    "duration": 1.209
  },
  {
    "text": "for people who have problems",
    "start": 9.175,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "with their windpipe.",
    "start": 10.51,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "But the problem is...",
    "start": 11.594,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "Paolo’s surgeries are failing.",
    "start": 13.513,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Paolo was selling a miracle.",
    "start": 16.891,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "People want to believe in a miracle.",
    "start": 18.643,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "But something is off.",
    "start": 22.23,
    "duration": 1.084
  },
  {
    "text": "He was just so desperate to",
    "start": 23.857,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "show this idea could work.",
    "start": 25.65,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And that had deadly consequences.",
    "start": 28.82,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Patient is developing all sorts of complications.",
    "start": 31.281,
    "duration": 2.794
  },
  {
    "text": "Paolo’s synthetic trachea clogs up.",
    "start": 34.701,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "The feeling that you’re about to suffocate",
    "start": 37.12,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "all the time.",
    "start": 38.955,
    "duration": 0.626
  },
  {
    "text": "It was medical torture.",
    "start": 41.875,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "He lied consistently throughout his career",
    "start": 45.17,
    "duration": 2.085
  },
  {
    "text": "about his credentials.",
    "start": 47.255,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Paolo was fooling everybody",
    "start": 49.382,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "professionally and personally.",
    "start": 50.842,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Macchiarini lied about",
    "start": 52.761,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "the success of the patients.",
    "start": 54.095,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "While Paolo’s patients were dying,",
    "start": 56.097,
    "duration": 1.877
  },
  {
    "text": "there were patients being actively recruited",
    "start": 58.516,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "and operated on.",
    "start": 60.643,
    "duration": 1.127
  },
  {
    "text": "He had to be stopped.",
    "start": 61.77,
    "duration": 1.293
  },
  {
    "text": "For me the question has always been...",
    "start": 63.646,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "How did he get away with it",
    "start": 67.025,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "for as long as he did?",
    "start": 68.401,
    "duration": 1.46
  }
]